ook（NASDAQ：FB）首席執行官馬克&middot;扎克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）將支持對Instagram和WhatsApp的收購，並表示該公司屬於改變世界的行業的一部分。 <br />\n<br />\nby Google翻譯"},{"pid":"0af9bf15717f0e02a2ea72462dc473b853e5ca7f","tid":2129550,"uid":221827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"如果再加埋m$同tesla<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"febb42c313c7aa24cca0604230edc21ea1860a83","tid":2129550,"uid":35820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"Microsoft無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb826beb777d604d1088f7ccaf61a10d1c9824f","tid":2129550,"uid":113074,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"febb42c313c7aa24cca0604230edc21ea1860a83","tid":2129550,"uid":35820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:34:52.000Z","msg":"Microsoft無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"M$被壟斷法勒索咗咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可以唞下"},{"pid":"ec9e62fec2282d4efed2740ff6c08a0674e71b7c","tid":2129550,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:37:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WBFDQvIrWYM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWBFDQvIrWYM&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD%2Bbr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=94fe48bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WBFDQvIrWYM</a><br />\n香港時間今晚12點"},{"pid":"d38d7df3ea388786d2deef6e2acd270fe00fc9f3","tid":2129550,"uid":275243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"73481ed349142470609367495e74d42a98c1f526","tid":2129550,"uid":321094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4100598bae1e5aee45b5eaf2fa8d4c22ddea422","tid":2129550,"uid":323720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3a434d78ed89d7baa8ddc2e841834c2a89fdbc6","tid":2129550